│ conversion) to skip the phi if `ExitSCEV` is a `SCEVCouldNotCompute`. The   │
│ edit should be in `llvm/lib/Transforms/Utils/ScalarEvolutionExpander.cpp`   │
│ at line 1243. We'll add:\n```cpp\n    if                                    │
│ (isa<SCEVCouldNotCompute>(ExitSCEV))\n      continue;\n```\nThis ensures we │
│ don't attempt to use a `CouldNotCompute` SCEV.\n\n5. Conclusion: The fix    │
│ prevents the crash by skipping phis that cannot be converted to integer     │
